      "emotion": "emotion: 驚き (surprise)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_03",
      "start_sec": 3.94,
      "duration": 2.68,
      "text": "“作り笑い”は前頭葉の異常と関係",
      "type": "title",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "002",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_04",
      "start_sec": 6.61,
      "duration": 2.08,
      "text": "過剰な作り笑いを繰り返す人には、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "002",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_05",
      "start_sec": 8.69,
      "duration": 1.41,
      "text": "前頭前野の活動が",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "002",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_06",
      "start_sec": 10.1,
      "duration": 1.26,
      "text": "低下しているケースがある。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "003",
      "emotion": "emotion: 悲しみ (sadness)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_07",
      "start_sec": 11.36,
      "duration": 1.74,
      "text": "これは情動制御の障害と",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "003",
      "emotion": "emotion: 悲しみ (sadness)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_08",
      "start_sec": 13.1,
      "duration": 0.86,
      "text": "関係しており、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "003",
      "emotion": "emotion: 悲しみ (sadness)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_09",
      "start_sec": 13.96,
      "duration": 1.67,
      "text": "社会的に不自然な言動を",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "004",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_10",
      "start_sec": 15.64,
      "duration": 1.33,
      "text": "引き起こす要因とされる。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "004",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_11",
      "start_sec": 16.97,
      "duration": 2.92,
      "text": "“常に笑顔”の人に違和感を覚えるのは正常",
      "type": "title",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "005",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_12",
      "start_sec": 19.89,
      "duration": 1.98,
      "text": "不自然な笑顔に対する違和感は、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "005",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_13",
      "start_sec": 21.88,
      "duration": 1.35,
      "text": "ヒトの警戒本能として",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "005",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_14",
      "start_sec": 23.23,
      "duration": 1.35,
      "text": "備わっているものとされる。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "006",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_15",
      "start_sec": 24.59,
      "duration": 1.92,
      "text": "表情と感情のズレを感じたとき、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "006",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_16",
      "start_sec": 26.51,
      "duration": 2.53,
      "text": "脳は“この人は危険かもしれない”と",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "006",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_17",
      "start_sec": 29.03,
      "duration": 1.21,
      "text": "自動的に判断する。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "007",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_18",
