      "duration": 1.35,
      "text": "“いい人そう”が",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "007",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_19",
      "start_sec": 31.59,
      "duration": 1.26,
      "text": "一番怖いこともある。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "007",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_20",
      "start_sec": 32.85,
      "duration": 2.71,
      "text": "笑いすぎる人は“脳腫瘍”の兆候も",
      "type": "title",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "008",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_21",
      "start_sec": 35.56,
      "duration": 2.53,
      "text": "前頭葉や側頭葉に腫瘍がある人の中に、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "008",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_22",
      "start_sec": 38.09,
      "duration": 1.74,
      "text": "理由のない笑いが出るケースがある。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "008",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_23",
      "start_sec": 39.83,
      "duration": 1.64,
      "text": "これは神経圧迫によって",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "009",
      "emotion": "emotion: 緊張 (tension)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_24",
      "start_sec": 41.47,
      "duration": 1.85,
      "text": "感情の抑制が効かなくなるためで、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "009",
      "emotion": "emotion: 緊張 (tension)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_25",
      "start_sec": 43.32,
